{"id": "EUVD-2024-3190", "enisaUuid": "30daa3ed-b60c-3c7f-85e0-0b06cbe6e0a7", "description": "The Salt-SSH pre-flight option copies the script to the target at a predictable path, which allows an attacker to force Salt-SSH to run their script. If an attacker has access to the target VM and knows the path to the pre-flight script before it runs they can ensure Salt-SSH runs their script with the privileges of the user running Salt-SSH.\u00a0Do not make the copy path on the target predictable and ensure we check return codes of the scp command if the copy fails.", "datePublished": "2024-11-14T04:13:55", "dateUpdated": "2024-11-14T15:20:15", "baseScore": 6.7, "baseScoreVersion": "3.1", "baseScoreVector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:L/AC:H/PR:L/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H", "references": ["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2023-34049", "https://github.com/saltstack/salt/commit/286d55eb5a6e6bf9428405bdf5632b419bdf8444", "https://github.com/saltstack/salt/commit/7a14112f2a16ce70e3c3e1862c92e37af5f2c7a4", "https://github.com/saltstack/salt", "https://saltproject.io/security-announcements/2023-10-27-advisory", "https://saltproject.io/security-announcements/2023-10-27-advisory/"], "aliases": ["CVE-2023-34049", "GHSA-4277-m35q-7c9w"], "assigner": "vmware", "epss": 0.05, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "72a7e573-2161-3771-92ac-19de9dc0b2aa", "product": {"name": "Salt"}, "product_version": "3004 <3006.4"}, {"id": "b261da86-d17f-3474-9f23-84ad97c69cf4", "product": {"name": "Salt"}, "product_version": "3005 <3005.4"}], "enisaIdVendor": [{"id": "c716a222-67d6-34fc-9d84-4169633a3312", "vendor": {"name": "Salt"}}], "isExploited": false}